body:
I was playing a Normal game because I was trying to get better at playing ADC with Caitlyn, I did pretty bad early game (I had a Yorick support that ended 0/11) so our Jax decided to start saying how bad we were and asking the enemy team to report me, so I basically said there is no reason to report someone if they have a bad game it is not an actual option in the report menu, as the closest to that is under &quot;Intentionally Feeding&quot; and I was not feeding on purpose, I started to do better in the late game but Jax still flamed me and by this time the Ezreal and Jayce also decided to flame me for feeding Quinn early game, the Soraka on the enemy team sided with me and said something along the lines of &quot;It&#039;s not his fault, you can&#039;t win every game.&quot; I asumed that  Jayce and Jax were premade because they started to lie in all chat saying I was flaming the entire game and being really toxic, even though I wasn&#039;t. This has happened a few times before, otherwise I wouldn&#039;t bother writing this. xD


If anyone could tell me if it&#039;s possible for me to get banned for getting false reported, and is it possible for someone who is false reporting to get banned for doing so, and encouraging other people to report me for no proper reason.

{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}
